## ğŸŒº FINAL SUMMARY TABLE

| Relationship    | Type           | UML Symbol          | Example            | Strength  |
| --------------- | -------------- | ------------------- | ------------------ | --------- |
| **Association** | uses-a         | Simple line (â€”)     | Teacherâ€“Department | Weak      |
| **Aggregation** | has-a          | Empty diamond (â—Š)   | Libraryâ€“Book       | Medium    |
| **Composition** | has-a (strong) | Filled diamond (â—†)  | Houseâ€“Room         | Strong    |
| **Inheritance** | is-a           | Arrow with triangle | Studentâ€“Person     | Strong    |
| **Dependency**  | temporary      | Dotted arrow        | Printerâ€“Document   | Very Weak |

